                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Police sergeant, K</hi> 35). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read: "Central Criminal Court, July, 1857; George Ward, Convicted for stealing lead; 
Confined six months."</hi>)—the prisoner is the person mentioned.</p>
